lar basis (think I sold 3 in 2 years) Maybe on other servers they do, but definitely not Torv that I have seen. <br>Sorry to rant so much, guess you just got me on a cranky day. ;-) <br>See you on the boards. <br></p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Just trying to be helpful.</td></tr>
